        <center><%= image_tag("social metric equn.jpg", :class => "img-responsive") %></center>
        <p>&nbsp;</p>
        <p>where a = importance of large numbers in social settings, where 1 is indifference, and 0 is great importance (this variable is <i>unique to each individual, but is constant across all of their calculations)</i></p>
        <p>This function increases the social metric for each person encountered that day but at a more comfortable rate which is specific to the individual. Satisfied with my new function, I was able to visually graph my social activity during the holiday month, post graduation.</p>
